in: 0px; padding: 2px 5px; background-color: rgb(245, 250, 254); text-align: right; width: 110px;\">重量</td>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 2px 5px;\">产品重量： 8KG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 750px; height: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g1/M03/00/04/rBEGDk-GbB0IAAAAAAKyeCqIucIAAAB0gHo-dQAArKQ013.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">麦博梵高FC230外观自然朴实，凝重庄严，黑色的主箱体被两侧采用棕色木纹贴皮的翼板包围着，没有什么花俏设计，古色古香，简洁大方而不失沉稳，符合成功人士的审美眼光；箱体采用了全木质结构，可以最大限度的避免谐振的产生，使得音质更加纯净。遥控设计，无论是配置给桌面电脑还是配置给客厅试听设备都能轻松应对。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 750px; height: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g2/M03/00/04/rBEGEE-GbDYIAAAAAAEbN8wlxsMAAAB0gEte1AAARtP898.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230具有遥控功能，麦博梵高FC230的遥控器除了静音和总音量控制外，还提供了输入切换和音色调节功能，其中高低音调节具有17级的调节范围。FC230设有AUX、PC两路音频输入，使用时同样也可以通过遥控器来进行切换选择。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 750px; height: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g4/M04/00/04/rBEGFk-GbIIIAAAAAAEo-d0MMRkAAAB0wEbT9sAASkR132.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230全木质的箱体采用长方体设计，深红色箱体与黑色面板的搭配，使产品显得大气而卓越不凡；没有过多的花俏设计，简洁大方又不失沉稳。同时也展现出厂家出色的制造工艺。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 750px; height: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g1/M03/00/04/rBEGDk-GbNoIAAAAAAFtGf-TmKUAAAB0gKbQWoAAW0x606.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230的主箱背部设计的条理分明，其倒相孔后置，在箱体上方偏右的位置。箱体中间位置是一大金属散热片。FC230的额定功率达到了56W，所以使用大散热片以加强功放芯片的散热。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 750px; height: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g1/M03/00/04/rBEGD0-GbSAIAAAAAAGGy_OP3XQAAAB0gLj_FgAAYbj589.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230单个音箱体积为205&times;165&times;265mm，体积虽然不是太大，却是很有分量。箱体采用了全木质结构，可以最大限度的避免谐振的产生，使得音质更加纯净。FC230主箱正面右下角是遥控器的红外线接收窗，里面除了红外接收头外，还有两个数码管用于显示音量数字。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 750px; height: auto;\"><img border=\"0\" class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g1/M03/00/04/rBEGD0-GbWQIAAAAAAF3AoGTJ-YAAAB0gMpg2kAAXca067.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230所有的控制键和插孔都设计在音箱的背板上面，使得音箱的这个外观简洁大方。其背部仅有音量调节，高音、低音调节功能可以通过遥控器来实现。FC230的音频信号输入插孔为RCA输入，副箱信号连接为塑胶接线柱，接线柱表面经过了镀金处理，并采用不同颜色的塑料外壳加以保护。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"442\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 7px; font-weight: bold; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230的扬声器单元采用了1英寸高音单元和4英寸低音单元的组合方式。4英寸PP盆低音单元，此种低音喇叭折环阻尼和宽度适中，无论是外观、手感还是工艺都是非常的出色，可见麦博的工艺水平不容小窥。低音喇叭再配合Microlab麦博独创之劲量低音重播技术，以低音扬声器单体设计和重低音箱体几何结构为基础，引用心理学理论，重放超乎预期的高质量低频响应，完美地展像了低音澎湃有力。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" height=\"210\" width=\"360\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g1/M05/00/04/rBEGD0-Gcc4IAAAAAADaAkiN8iwAAAB1ACdlrEAANoa742.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230的高音单元采用了著名扬声器设计师Peter Larsen最新研发的软球顶高音T9，这可以从副箱下方金黄色的激光标贴看出。这个高音单元所采用的振膜为&ldquo;摩雷&rdquo;音膜，其听感细腻柔和，延展性出色，完美展现了高音通透亮丽。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" height=\"210\" width=\"360\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g2/M05/00/04/rBEGEE-GceoIAAAAAAG-iD6aCywAAAB1AB0IbIAAb6g959.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n            <td width=\"442\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 7px; font-weight: bold; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\">分频器</div>\r\n            <div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 15px 15px 15px 7px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\'; text-indent: 2em;\">FC230的电路元件设计比较整洁，其采用了两层板设计，左侧的是电源供应及后级放大电路部分，右侧为信号输入部分。设计师还在220V交流电输入的地方设计了一个磁环用于消除干扰。为了给前级运放芯片及遥控电力等提供稳定的电压供应而使用了两颗稳压三极管。麦博FC230使用的前级芯片为NE5532P，后级设计比较特殊，与麦博的其它产品一样采用了IGBT功放管的设计，这种设计是多媒体领域中非常罕见了，保证了电路的稳定性和音质的质量。其额定功率可达到56W，可以说是目前4英寸单元的2.0箱中最大的产品了。</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"750\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; empty-cells: show; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\'; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" height=\"210\" width=\"360\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img class=\"err-product\" src=\"http://img30.360buyimg.com/erpWareDetail/g1/M05/00/04/rBEGD0-GcXIIAAAAAAIvsxWzOCUAAAB1AAs2N4AAi_L676.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repea